ng-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</link><description>一位美国官员预计延迟不会持续超过几天。然而，另一位人士指出，周五之后的任何拖延都将不可避免地被视为拜登政府“做假账”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-miss-deadline-on-reporting-whether-israel-violating-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和他的帮派更喜欢死去的人质，而不是快乐的左翼分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</link><description>战争已经过去七个月了，将这个以色列邪教成员团结在一起的唯一粘合剂仍然是对任何他们认为是“左派”的事物的深不可测的仇恨</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡上周推动拉法攻势，以色列战时内阁反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理的一些行为暗示了推迟达成协议的不可告人的动机。他的办公室否认了此类指控，但尽管以色列官员评估哈马斯即将同意该提议，但内塔尼亚胡不顾战时内阁的反对，开始准备在拉法采取军事行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的加沙人来说，离开拉法就是从一个地狱走向另一个地狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-gazans-leaving-rafah-is-moving-from-one-hell-to-another/0000018f-5411-d348-a7bf-f6b95e5a0000</link><description>以色列军队最近发动了加沙居民的撤离，他们被迫在汗尤尼斯废墟和没有供水和污水基础设施的沿海地带之间做出选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 0